title: Requirements Gathering Recap
summary: This meeting focuses on the requirements gathering process for accessing NextGen and discusses billing and claims information. Participants share insights on service codes, payer modifications, and the need for a consolidated spreadsheet to streamline the billing process.

Overview of spreadsheet requirements for billing rules
Clarification on CPT codes and billing practices
Emphasis on the need for a consolidated claims template
